          Privacy Policy for AFC Hymns Collection
Effective Date: 20 November 2024
Last Updated: 26 November 2024
Welcome to the AFC Hymns Collection app. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal and sensitive data. We are committed to maintaining the privacy and security of our users. By using the AFC Hymns Collection app, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
________________________________________
1. About Us
The AFC Hymns Collection app is developed and managed by Strivemore Tapera, Joseph Jaravani, and the AFC Media Team. Our mission is to provide a rich hymnal experience while ensuring compliance with privacy regulations, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) where applicable.
